The feeling of love is also fragrant.

373
00:41:01,917 --> 00:41:05,217
声も 顔も 不器用なとこも
Your voice, your face, your awkward side...

374
00:41:06,217 --> 00:41:13,317
全部 全部 大嫌いだよ
I hate it all, I hate it all.

375
00:41:14,117 --> 00:41:18,217
まだ枯れない花を君に添えてさ
