376
00:41:18,617 --> 00:41:23,117
ずっと ずっと ずっと ずっと
always, always, always, always...

377
00:41:23,217 --> 00:41:29,517
抱えてよ
please hold on to it.

378
00:41:33,117 --> 00:41:38,117
ずっと ずっと...
Always, always...

379
